{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be modern and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SaaS Product - Revolutionize Your Workflow</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935;\n            --secondary-color: #f48fb1;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-footer-bg: #fdecea;\n            --button-hover-bg: #d32f2f;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        header .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 25px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--button-hover-bg);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            text-align: left;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border: 1px solid #eeeeee;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            box-sha