-background-color); color: var(--brand-color);\">Choose Plan</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\" style=\"background-color: var(--background-color); border: none;\">\n                    <h3 style=\"color: var(--brand-color); font-size: 1.8em;\">Enterprise</h3>\n                    <p style=\"font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Contact Us</p>\n                    <p>Custom solutions for large organizations.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; background-color: var(--brand-color); color: var(--background-color);\">Contact Sales</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or need a custom solution? We're here to help.</p>\n            <form action=\"#\" style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; text-align: left;\">\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    <label for=\"name\" style=\"display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Name</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" style=\"width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    <label for=\"email\" style=\"display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Email</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" style=\"width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                </div>\n                <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n                    <label for=\"message\" style=\"display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;\">Message</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"6\" style=\"width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px;\"></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"display: block; width: 100%; background-color: var(--brand-color); color: var(--background-color); padding: 15px;\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 SaaSify. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Built with <span style=\"color: var(--brand-color);\">Red</span> and Passion.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}